---
title: Rio Rancho Pulled Pork Tacos Dinner’s Just 15 Minutes Away!
description: Is there anything better than pulled pork? Why yes: this marvelous Tex-Mex mash-up! Here, we’ve #putitinataco (let’s get that trending) to make all your dinner dreams a reality. The pork is topped with a tangy, vinegary cabbage slaw and hot sauce crema to amp up the bold flavor and add delicious crunch. One bite will have your tastebuds yelling “yeehaw!”
